headline: 2 Popular AI Stocks to Sell Before They Fall 55% and 68% in 2025, According to Certain Wall Street Analysts
summary: Shares of Palantir Technologies (NASDAQ: PLTR) advanced 1,110% during the last two years as the company benefited from strong demand for its artificial intelligence platform.  The median target of $39 per share implies 52% downside from its current share price of $80.  Brad Zelnick at Deutsche Bank is particularly bearish on Palantir.
